select count(*) as aggregate from `tbl_client_event` left join `tbl_client` on `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`client_id` left join `tbl_events` on `tbl_events`.`event_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`event_id` left join `tbl_lead` on `tbl_lead`.`lead_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`lead_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_corp` on `tbl_corp`.`corp_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`partner_id` where `tbl_client_event`.`client_id` = '1503'

select `tbl_client_event`.`clientevent_id`, `tbl_events`.`event_title` as `event_name`, `tbl_client_event`.`joined_date`, `tbl_client_event`.`status`, `tbl_events`.`event_startdate`, (CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT("KOL: ", tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN CONCAT(tbl_eduf_lead.title)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Partners" THEN CONCAT(tbl_corp.corp_name)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END) AS conversion_lead, CONCAT(tbl_client.first_name," ", COALESCE(tbl_client.last_name, "")) as client_name from `tbl_client_event` left join `tbl_client` on `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`client_id` left join `tbl_events` on `tbl_events`.`event_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`event_id` left join `tbl_lead` on `tbl_lead`.`lead_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`lead_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_corp` on `tbl_corp`.`corp_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`partner_id` where `tbl_client_event`.`client_id` = '1503'
